snippet.title: Qisah Tomang: Cycle Ends STEAM Next Fest Trailer
snippet.description:
East Asian Themed Classic Short JRPG, Untangle the shrouded multidimensional threat in the middle of conflict between Warlords.

Play the Demo now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2227810/Qisah_Tomang_Cycle_Ends/?utm_source=homepage&utm_campaign=NEXTFESTYT&utm_medium=web

A new demo is released for #steamnextfest event, give it  a try and please send us your feedback!
